**üéØ Human Intervention and AI Work Effort Tracking Architecture**

## Core Tracking Categories

### 1. **Human Intervention Types**
```typescript
interface HumanIntervention {
  id: string;
  sessionId: string;
  devlogId: DevlogId;
  timestamp: string;

  // Intervention classification
  type: 'clarification' | 'decision' | 'guidance' | 'correction' | 'unblock' | 'approval';
  trigger: 'ai-request' | 'ai-stuck' | 'error-escalation' | 'quality-check' | 'scheduled';
  severity: 'minor' | 'moderate' | 'major' | 'critical';

  // Context and impact
  description: string;
  aiAttempts: number;           // How many times AI tried before intervention
  contextTokens: number;        // Tokens used before intervention
  timeToIntervention: number;   // Minutes from start to intervention
  resolutionTime: number;       // Minutes human spent resolving

  // Outcome tracking
  outcome: 'resolved' | 'redirected' | 'escalated' | 'deferred';
  followUpRequired: boolean;
  lessonsLearned: string[];
}
```

### 2. **AI Work Session Tracking**
```typescript
interface AIWorkSession {
  id: string;
  devlogId: DevlogId;
  startTime: string;
  endTime?: string;

  // Effort measurements
  totalTokensUsed: number;
  contextRebuildTokens: number;
  toolCallsCount: number;
  iterationCount: number;

  // Autonomy metrics
  humanInterventions: HumanIntervention[];
  autonomyScore: number;        // 0-100% autonomous work
  successRate: number;          // Did session achieve goals?
  efficiencyScore: number;      // Tokens/outcome ratio

  // Session outcomes
  tasksCompleted: string[];
  problemsSolved: string[];
  contextBuilt: string[];
  knowledgeGained: string[];
  blockers: string[];
}
```

### 3. **Autonomy Analytics**
```typescript
interface AutonomyMetrics {
  devlogId: DevlogId;
  timeframe: 'session' | 'daily' | 'weekly' | 'project';

  // Core autonomy indicators
  humanInterventionRate: number;    // % of time requiring human help
  zeroTouchOperationTime: number;   // Minutes of continuous AI work
  autonomousTaskCompletionRate: number; // % tasks completed without help

  // Efficiency metrics
  averageSessionLength: number;
  contextRebuildRatio: number;      // Context tokens / total tokens
  iterationsToSuccess: number;

  // Trend analysis
  improvementTrend: 'improving' | 'stable' | 'declining';
  interventionPatterns: string[];
  optimizationOpportunities: string[];
}
```

